briefdescription.para: primal heuristic that tries a given solution

detaileddescription.para: Marc Pfetsch This heuristic takes a solution from somewhere else via the function SCIPheurPassSolTrySol(). It then tries to commit this solution. It is mainly used by cons_indicator, which tries to correct a given solution, but cannot directly submit this solution, because it is a constraint handler and not a heuristic.
